OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine end
OL,6,Fto the day with hazy evening sunshine
OL,7,Fand staying dry overnight with
OL,8,Fvariable cloud cover. Winds will be
OL,9,Flight and perhaps some mistiness
OL,10,Faround East Lothian coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FMainly dry and bright with
OL,13,Fhazy sunshine and very warm or hot.
OL,14,FLight winds with sea breezes. Isolated
OL,15,Fheavy showers possible in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
